data-raw/publications/**/*.pdf

# R Markdown render / preview artifacts (we commit the .md, never the .html)
# *.html
# *_files/
# *_cache/

# Legacy GitHub-wiki build output (publish to the separate .wiki repo, not here)
data-raw/publications/risk-management/wiki/

# Scratch / leftover folders
**/hold/
